{"tid":374190,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單自己整乳酪","createTime":"2017-08-25T14:32:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-29T03:15:18.000Z","uid":18117,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e687e72c77dd3bb19572ba9701c15ea15774fd10","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:32:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/222250_6c0c708149b91e47472c88fd204833ef.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F222250_6c0c708149b91e47472c88fd204833ef.jpg&h=38b043b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n材料 原味乳酪 奶 密實玻璃樽 碗仔 匙羹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/222250_5f302335bc5ba7bb8d5168fad595616f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F222250_5f302335bc5ba7bb8d5168fad595616f.jpg&h=9a65860d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開一大盆水 滾水消毒下啲工具先 <br />\n滾佢幾分鐘<br />\n之後我就放焗爐烘番乾佢 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/222251_9287a2a0b67fada42ce23264fcaa5d16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F222251_9287a2a0b67fada42ce23264fcaa5d16.jpg&h=619d5d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n將杯乳酪倒落碗仔先 落少少奶攪暈<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/25/222252_9287a2a0b67fada42ce23264fcaa5d16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F25%2F222252_9287a2a0b67fada42ce23264fcaa5d16.jpg&h=82d4eae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後全部材料倒哂落去玻璃樽度<br />\n頭先啲滾水仲暖 我用黎坐熱佢<br />\n由佢發酵7-9個鐘就食得<br />\n<br />\n搞掂 聽朝有乳酪食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3eb7df6c5ecf89b738fcbc610c3f1b26c486df2","tid":374190,"uid":120908,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:35:16.000Z","msg":"用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f285a5d1a7aa0b4447bb4075f4fd052c104d47cf","tid":374190,"uid":126436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> lm"},{"pid":"2e6d96fd4d341cbba7be5c4d6766e6a08efd4898","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:40:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平一半有多 依度等於十幾杯<br />\n食剩少少 加盒奶 <br />\n重覆以上步驟就可以繼續整<br />\n重點係冇咁多添加劑 <br />\n少糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c435de55862fedb2133a087a1d9475babd433ba9","tid":374190,"uid":122264,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"樓主下次可以教整朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d6e37dff74097734b95492c29d5164bc756e9f","tid":374190,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:48:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平一半有多 依度等於十幾杯<br />\n食剩少少 加盒奶 <br />\n重覆以上步驟就可以繼續整<br />\n重點係冇咁多添加劑 <br />\n少糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁整完第日再加奶，係咪可以無限loop?"},{"pid":"4c2ec57f6ebe4f78d1ec761455c836dd8b72b5ab","tid":374190,"uid":120908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平一半有多 依度等於十幾杯<br />\n食剩少少 加盒奶 <br />\n重覆以上步驟就可以繼續整<br />\n重點係冇咁多添加劑 <br />\n少糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁整完第日再加奶，係咪可以無限loop?</blockquote><br />\n唔會到期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"065e4ecf6b3afcc80a7d8f03bb4b2b146d94a6db","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n平一半有多 依度等於十幾杯<br />\n食剩少少 加盒奶 <br />\n重覆以上步驟就可以繼續整<br />\n重點係冇咁多添加劑 <br />\n少糖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁整完第日再加奶，係咪可以無限loop?</blockquote><br />\n唔會到期？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d26a204f73a883c32ac0eea752240546bc8555","tid":374190,"uid":4453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T18:41:13.000Z","msg":"巴打就咁放喺煲水8個鐘？<br />\n唔會變涷咩？聽講要恒溫嘅<br />\n我都想試下自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想請教下yogurt 同奶嘅比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48524a7ed037340140bbc95f86dcbdeefe77e4b3","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T23:10:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打就咁放喺煲水8個鐘？<br />\n唔會變涷咩？聽講要恒溫嘅<br />\n我都想試下自己整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想請教下yogurt 同奶嘅比例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實奶可以用慢火煮熱到45度先<br />\n不過我廢事洗多樣野所以直接放落熱水坐熱<br />\n<br />\n會變凍架但夏天室溫都已經夠發酵<br />\n你放入電飯煲開著保暖mode都得<strong></strong><br />\n<br />\n份量答你唔到<br />\n整過幾次都係一杯140g乳酪配1L奶<br />\n印象中睇過啲食譜係可以落少啲"},{"pid":"58900e54839ac127772db00b59dc913c3742f0ab","tid":374190,"uid":1556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T23:27:55.000Z","msg":"上網睇過樓望講既野<br />\n<br />\n不過成日都諗，d 乳酪同牛奶應該『愈溝愈稀』先係，整多幾劑之後個d 仲係咪乳酪，定得個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f008f43331ffd2c56b5c3968393b9afefd2bb8e","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:34:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網睇過樓望講既野<br />\n<br />\n不過成日都諗，d 乳酪同牛奶應該『愈溝愈稀』先係，整多幾劑之後個d 仲係咪乳酪，定得個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都係買一次整一次唔會留種<br />\n同你諗法一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999d4f93c78fdfe26fa6dd0b609286c44e2d5311","tid":374190,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:43:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩嘢"},{"pid":"97f186ccd964fb80b1afb757ebb1c73c6584ffab","tid":374190,"uid":51889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為乳酪入面有乳酸菌，所以可以將牛奶變乳酪<br />\n唔想乳酪整乳酪，可以買一包包嘅乳酸菌整都得"},{"pid":"558b2d7900ff8d8237444826f16f6b22e0933d4d","tid":374190,"uid":41315,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:54:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係咁樣整架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後佢係制造緊一個適當既環境由佢個種成長<br />\n原理就同 用蘋果種蘋果樹差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85d9aa9a85bf7384d80e23047ebef0509813e4f6","tid":374190,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:54:08.000Z","msg":"買個yogurt maker 啦，你開咁大煲水去坐，效果仲要無咁好。<br />\n同埋咁樣整最好再生十次左右就要換種。"},{"pid":"017743415d5a75873e64d039ad900e7c70e73147","tid":374190,"uid":51889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上網睇過樓望講既野<br />\n<br />\n不過成日都諗，d 乳酪同牛奶應該『愈溝愈稀』先係，整多幾劑之後個d 仲係咪乳酪，定得個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會愈整愈稀<br />\n當乳酸菌分解牛奶入面嘅乳糖，就會分泌出乳酸<br />\n乳酸會降低ph值，令牛奶變得凝固<br />\n只要有乳酸菌，有適當溫度<br />\n牛奶就可以變乳酪"},{"pid":"789eded640eb40511752a8b05ef47578d88a59e4","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:58:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/085452_ede738e4a774a84404d3ae5ba997cb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F085452_ede738e4a774a84404d3ae5ba997cb2e.jpg&h=a598289a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食落冇出面買既咁傑但係滑好多<br />\n味道就係原味無糖乳酪咁樣"},{"pid":"6c12e4b283719f98478f4342f34e17ec9170cc40","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:04:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買個yogurt maker 啦，你開咁大煲水去坐，效果仲要無咁好。<br />\n同埋咁樣整最好再生十次左右就要換種。</blockquote><br />\n近排買左好多廚房野<br />\n買多舊野肯定又比老母屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夏天暫時咁整效果ok架 <br />\n但冬天買部係真係方便啲既<br />\n有冇邊隻牌子推介<br />\n遲啲考慮買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2509aeab05d1f58289c4f7398ba18332f603ebfc","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:07:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩嘢</blockquote><br />\n冇玩野呀弘B 真係咁整<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f83012dc1080418be9e3a0c6058c2acbf8f8787","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用乳酪整乳酪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係咁樣整架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其後佢係制造緊一個適當既環境由佢個種成長<br />\n原理就同 用蘋果種蘋果樹差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉樓上有人叫我用朱古力整朱古力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"540b47d11a869aefb06648439eb184d23934dea2","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>上網睇過樓望講既野<br />\n<br />\n不過成日都諗，d 乳酪同牛奶應該『愈溝愈稀』先係，整多幾劑之後個d 仲係咪乳酪，定得個樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔會愈整愈稀<br />\n當乳酸菌分解牛奶入面嘅乳糖，就會分泌出乳酸<br />\n乳酸會降低ph值，令牛奶變得凝固<br />\n只要有乳酸菌，有適當溫度<br />\n牛奶就可以變乳酪</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7790f6f2ba6e9f1c3d19c2b5e8f8d56a221b182","tid":374190,"uid":17425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>買個yogurt maker 啦，你開咁大煲水去坐，效果仲要無咁好。<br />\n同埋咁樣整最好再生十次左右就要換種。</blockquote><br />\n近排買左好多廚房野<br />\n買多舊野肯定又比老母屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n夏天暫時咁整效果ok架 <br />\n但冬天買部係真係方便啲既<br />\n有冇邊隻牌子推介<br />\n遲啲考慮買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYoghurt maker 細過你依家個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你要平既有保溫壺既款，認真做就一係買做出黎獨立一罐罐，一係用麵包機，佢地有恆溫去做yoghurt."},{"pid":"e14a2c5d90395f734074fb03b54de34901420b38","tid":374190,"uid":17425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/085452_ede738e4a774a84404d3ae5ba997cb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F085452_ede738e4a774a84404d3ae5ba997cb2e.jpg&h=a598289a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食落冇出面買既咁傑但係滑好多<br />\n味道就係原味無糖乳酪咁樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用機整啦，你呢個樣未form 好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/091409_7a8c17c2c937345e8e293fefbb794d8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F091409_7a8c17c2c937345e8e293fefbb794d8c.jpg&h=47232788&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2a3ffb3fbaff9a142c0f220e874f51841b03b363","tid":374190,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T01:17:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/085452_ede738e4a774a84404d3ae5ba997cb2e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F085452_ede738e4a774a84404d3ae5ba997cb2e.jpg&h=a598289a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食落冇出面買既咁傑但係滑好多<br />\n味道就係原味無糖乳酪咁樣</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 用機整啦，你呢個樣未form 好<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/26/091409_7a8c17c2c937345e8e293fefbb794d8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F26%2F091409_7a8c17c2c937345e8e293fefbb794d8c.jpg&h=47232788&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食完依碗再擺係度發酵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}